  <acronym>CHIMOVIP</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized Study Assessing Two Strategies of First Line: a Strategy With Intraperitoneal Chemotherapy and a Strategy With Total Intravenous Strategy, in Patients With Epithelial Advanced Ovarian Cancer</official_title>
