  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      CHIMOVIP is a study to determine the best therapeutic strategy in patient with ovarian
      advanced cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized phase II study, open-label and multicentric. After initial intervention
      (debulking surgery or diagnostic surgery) patient will randomized in the study according to
      Completeness of cytoreduction (CC) score (CC0 or CC&gt;1).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
